{"id":794178940,"lang":"python","lang_name":"Python","time":"10 months, 2 weeks","timestamp":1662581864,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"81 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/794178940/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"14.2 MB","code":"class Solution(object):\n    def lengthOfLongestSubstring(self, s):\n        \"\"\"\n        :type s: str\n        :rtype: int\n        \"\"\"\n        #step 1 - create a set\n        charSet = set()\n        #create the return variable\n        res = 0\n        # create left pointer to 0\n        l = 0\n        #iterate over string\n        for r in range(len(s)):\n            # while the character is a duplicate, smallen the sliding window\n            while s[r] in charSet:\n                charSet.remove(s[l])\n                l+=1\n            charSet.add(s[r])\n            res = max(res, r-l+1)\n        return res\n                \n            \n        ","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false}
